item.value: Flirty Dancing 2x06 "Dan & Anna and Seretta & Steven"

content.html:
Ashley Banjo arranges for country boy and rugby fan Dan and 24-year-old Polish woman Anna to come together for an intimate and flirty routine in Williamson Park, Lancashire. Dance lover and divorcee Seretta is paired with Steven, a 64-year-old account manager who moved to Cambridge, also following a divorce. Ashley choreographs a romantic dance, full of fun, with the spectacular backdrop of a lavender field at sunset.
